      "width": 400,
      "height": 290,
      "text": "📁 medical-knowledge/  (JSON only)\n\n📂 cancers/breast/\n   cancer-info.json, treatments.json,\n   side-effects.json, education/\n\n📂 drugs/\n   chemo-agents.json, immunotherapy.json,\n   interactions/cyp450-matrix.json\n\n📂 supplements/evidence-database.json\n📂 radiotherapy/protocols.json\n📂 surgery/procedures.json\n📂 reference-ranges/blood-markers.json\n📂 medical-terms/pl.json, en.json, de.json\n📂 patient-experience/chemo-patterns/",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
