      "x": 515,
      "y": 335,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 290,
      "text": "📁 src/  (TypeScript only)\n\n📂 lib/medical-data/\n   knowledge-registry.ts ← imports JSONs\n   disease-matcher.ts    ← matches diagnosis\n   content-utils.ts      ← localized() helper\n\n📂 lib/\n   system-prompt.ts  ← AI instructions\n   input-guard.ts    ← security (injection)\n   pii-sanitizer.ts  ← privacy filter\n   db.ts             ← IndexedDB (local)\n\n📂 components/\n   chat/, notebook/, calendar/,\n   education/, settings/, imaging/",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "baseline": 280,
